column1: #Text=DS : You 're forced to choose between having either India or China blown off the face of the Earth , and if you do n't choose , they both go .
#Text=They are equal in population according to the 2000 census in each country , with each having roughly 1.2 billion people .
#Text=Sune : You would choose India because your grandparents are from China !
#Text=No , to me , India is a democracy , it 's the world 's largest democracy and I 've been there .
#Text=I found it be a really spiritual place .
#Text=Some of the most intelligent people I have ever met are from India .
#Text=And China , I have to say , not so much .
#Text=I have only been to the countryside .
#Text=My grandfather is Chinese as well ; I 'm a quarter Chinese .
#Text=I just think they are more barbaric by their culture ... .
#Text=Sune : [ Shaking his head ] We 're never going to tour China now ... .
#Text=DS : You would go with China too , then ?
#Text=Sune : I 'm not going to choose ... you can blow them both up !
#Text=Sune : Well , I mean , I do n't know , come on ... I 'll go with Sharin , then .

#Text=DS : Sharin , you have a choice between either dating a man who is losing it hair and he tries to style the remaining hair artistically to cover it up , or you have a choice of dating a man with man boobs --

#Text=And actually his breasts were pretty nice .
